{"tid":924920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泥頭車上同男友吵大鑊 烈女觀塘繞道跳車重創","createTime":"2018-12-02T12:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T13:28:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":819,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"29bd069b817dc1df1a21048c0692ef5e88f77289","tid":924920,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543752410_dcde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543752410_dcde.jpg&h=d210ca08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名泥頭車司機駕車載同女友商談感情事，詎料發生爭吵，當車駛經觀塘繞道期間，女子一時氣忿竟然打開車門跳落橋面受傷倒地，幸好未有車輛緊貼而行，否則可能被車輛撞到。一輛尾隨的士「車Cam」拍下 那一幕驚險跳車情景，片段顯示女子跳落橋邊位置，再跳遠少許就會「跌落橋」，後果堪虞。<br />\n<br />\n跳車受傷30歲女子姓曾，頸部及手部受傷，其男友姓文(33歲)。事發上周四(29日)下午近4時，文駕泥頭車載同曾女沿觀塘繞道慢線東行，當駛至勵業街附近時，兩人疑為感情問題起爭拗，爭吵間，曾女突然打開左邊車門，然後蹤身躍落近橋邊的橋面，當場受傷倒地，幸好當時無車輛緊隨泥頭車，文發現女友跳車亦即停車報警，由救護車將她送院救治。警方將案件列作糾紛及交通意外有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n烈女？傻西咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fc247880ee22b5ab09b808260ef10bf7b196f0","tid":924920,"uid":185092,"like":278,"dislike":2,"score":276,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"智障"},{"pid":"cc19e664fb55a7c96b5ab58229f1bac75e7b0263","tid":924920,"uid":146435,"like":588,"dislike":1,"score":587,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"烈女不怕死"},{"pid":"9e5c1687c3bb2f3300bc305ef6a94da4c9bd501c","tid":924920,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35156040afc3a06e9db9c6fea4f49778d54e9022","tid":924920,"uid":6192,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"勇者無懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"